Package commandLineApplication

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameEnvironment
    Class the game is run from
    Island
    Island is either home or destination for a ship.
    Item
    Items that are available to buy or sell by the player from/to a store when visiting the island
    Items includes food and weapons
    Pirates
    A type of the random events player may meet while sailing
    RandomEvent
    Super class of random events that can heppen during a sail
    RescueSailors
    A type of the random events player may meet while sailing
    Route
    The path thet the player can take from the island they are based to another island
    There are 2 different routes connecting 2 random islands, in total there are 20 routes in the systems
    Ship
    Ship is the vehicle to travel from an island to the other
    There are 4 ships for player to choose from
    Store
    Store is a place to trade good for player
    There are 5 stores in total, each is situated in a unique island
    Weather
    A type of the random events player may meet while sailing
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InsufficientCoinsException
    This class is used when the user runs out of coins to continue purchasing or sailing
    InsufficientInventorySpaceException
    This Exception class shows message when there is no more space for inventory
    ItemNotOwnedException
    This Exception class shows message player wants to sell/ use an item that he does not own
